{"tid":522860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收工男叫開公民廣場？ 反撃譚耀宗靠劉細良","createTime":"2018-01-08T03:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T08:20:53.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0289e27ae9d5144fe3058849f4b0255d8fd741fd","tid":522860,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"公民廣場去年年尾「重開」，平日朝6晚11開放，恢復作為政府總部的車輛通道及上落客地點，以及訪客及職員的通道，遊行或集會須先向行政署申請並只限於星期日及公眾假期。港台節目《城市論壇》今午首度移師至公民廣場舉行，節目甫開始已充滿火藥味，全國政協委員譚耀宗指，「呢度唔係公民廣場，係政府東翼入口，俾車出入嘅。有限度開放作為通道出入係好嘅」，即被台下噓爆。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志主席羅冠聰指，所謂重開公民廣場是言過其實，「市民都無辦法有自由咁入嚟進行政治示威，圍欄全部都係封死晒。要真正重開，就應該拆晒啲圍欄」。<br />\n<br />\n中央政策組前顧問劉細良則批評，當年圍封公民廣場，時任政務司司長林鄭月娥亦有份作決定，諷刺林鄭現時重開公民廣場，「有咩比（前特首）梁振英好？就係扮開放」。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180108/20268251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F20268251&d=Obgldri6mh5%2FSbhtWCMOBr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2675d367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F20268251&h=5702c085\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180108/20268251</a>"},{"pid":"467ccb2c4798498ea3f0197e9ffb495dbb5470f2","tid":522860,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77f208e020b1a2082090a3ba885d1478a656770","tid":522860,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}